            <div>
               <h2> Julian Jara-Ettinger </h2>
			   <p> is a graduate student in ECCL studying Theory of Mind (ToM), our capacity to attribute unobservable mental states (like desires and intentions) to agents.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
	
